dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase NVilas_Zoning_2017.gdbN. The features included in this geodatabase are NVilas_Airport_2017N, NVilas_General_2017N, and NVilas_Shoreland_2017N.
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Vilas County Land Information and Mapping Department
dc_subject_sm: Zoning - Maps, City Planning, County Ordinances
